princeton_ansible.title: EZproxy Geolite DB download should go to a stable directory

comments.body: I think this one can be closed.
@kayiwa if an application is running a different desired_nodejs_version where will I overwrite this?

@eliotjordan is this still a concern? Most if not all of our roles are idempotent now - certainly the `deploy_user` role can be run multiple times without any destructive behavior. If you're concerned about the geoserver app directory, I'd be happy to pair up and run the playbook with appropriate precautions, and fix anything in the playbook that turns out to be destructive on a second run.
